title: EAGLE MENTALITY

description:
The Mentality of an Eagle will change your life. When life gets hard, be the eagle, soar above the clouds and push through the storms of your life. This is a New Motivational Speech spoken by Eddie Pinero (https://bit.ly/EddiePineroMotiversity).
